Package: redlistr
Title: Tools for the IUCN Red List of Ecosystems and Species
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Nicholas", "Murray", email = "murr.nick@gmail.com", role = c("cre","aut")))
Description: A toolbox for calculating the metrics required for assessing
    species under the International Union for Conservation of Nature (IUCN) Red List
    of Threatened Species and ecosystems under the IUCN Red List of Ecosystems. See
    the IUCN website for detailed guidelines on assessing the criteria, assessments,
    and other information.
Imports:
    raster, rgeos
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.4)
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
